{"tid":1366670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［暗角七警］兩人獲撤銷定罪　其餘五人減刑","createTime":"2019-07-26T04:28:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T04:46:20.000Z","uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6edbc59d4c2fb05758b1082d828008cde89b33e8","tid":1366670,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:28:46.000Z","msg":"7名警員涉於2014年佔領在金鐘襲擊曾健超，被告均不服定罪及刑期判決，提出上訴，高院上訴庭去年11月開庭處理後，今日（7月26日）裁定劉興沛及黃偉豪2人上訴得直，獲撤銷定罪，另外5五人上訴被駁回，維持定罪，但獲減刑。 <br />\n<br />\n獲減刑的5人當中，黃祖成及劉卓毅由監禁24個月減至18個月，白榮斌及關嘉豪囚15個月，陳少丹囚16個月，5人須即時服刑。 <br />\n<br />\n7名被告包括：<br />\n有組織罪案及三合會調查科總督察黃祖成，<br />\n觀塘區反黑組高級督察劉卓毅，<br />\n觀塘區反黑組警長白榮斌，<br />\n反黑組警員劉興沛、黃偉豪，<br />\n東九龍總區刑事總部警員陳少丹，<br />\n九龍城區刑事偵緝警員關嘉豪。<br />\n<br />\n七警於2017年2月在區域法院被裁定襲擊致造成身體傷害罪成，各被判監兩年，各人服刑百多日後，陸續獲准保釋，等候上訴。<br />\n<br />\n熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-26-2019/54620\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F07-26-2019%2F54620&d=AixoiqhHuTrv0%2F0Xa%2FX9x6pJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=481e7b09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-26-2019/54620</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2019"},{"pid":"9c19dbc86f64dfa57634780b053869934b021571","tid":1366670,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:37:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f39e646b03064be26d39fec8287ea065531b414c","tid":1366670,"uid":238138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:39:55.000Z","msg":"so fucking angry"},{"pid":"e4daff0d5a5480e5ef29478ee621ea13154059ff","tid":1366670,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:40:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"926f751f821880171d11e76708bac64ae9335394","tid":1366670,"uid":82947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:40:50.000Z","msg":"727元朗見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},